#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn10.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Indaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Maṇibhaddasutta "
msgstr "4. With Maṇibhadda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn10.4:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā magadhesu viharati maṇimālike cetiye maṇibhaddassa yakkhassa bhavane. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Magadhans at the Maṇimālika tree shrine, the haunt of the native spirit Maṇibhadda. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.4:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho maṇibhaddo yakkho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then the native spirit Maṇibhadda went up to the Buddha, and recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2, verse-num-sc812
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.1"
msgid "“Satīmato sadā bhaddaṃ, "
msgstr "“It’s always auspicious for the mindful; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.2"
msgid "satimā sukhamedhati; "
msgstr "the mindful prosper in happiness. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.3"
msgid "Satīmato suve seyyo, "
msgstr "Each new day is better for the mindful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:2.4"
msgid "verā ca parimuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "and they’re freed from enmity.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.448, sc3, verse-num-sc813
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.1"
msgid "“Satīmato sadā bhaddaṃ, "
msgstr "“It’s always auspicious for the mindful; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.2"
msgid "satimā sukhamedhati; "
msgstr "the mindful prosper in happiness. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.3"
msgid "Satīmato suve seyyo, "
msgstr "Each new day is better for the mindful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:3.4"
msgid "verā na parimuccati. "
msgstr "but they’re not freed from enmity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4, verse-num-sc814
#. VAR: sabbamahorattaṃ → sabbamahorrattiṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.1"
msgid "Yassa sabbamahorattaṃ, "
msgstr "But someone whose mind delights in harmlessness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.2"
msgid "ahiṃsāya rato mano; "
msgstr "all day and all night, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.3"
msgid "Mettaṃso sabbabhūtesu, "
msgstr "with love for all living creatures—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.4:4.4"
msgid "veraṃ tassa na kenacī”ti. "
msgstr "they have no enmity for anyone.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
